; ================================================================
; CITYSCAPE — procedural building forest via MultiMesh
; Generated at runtime by cityscape.gd. Ground at Y=-80,
; thousands of buildings, 4 draw calls total.
; S/W/E: tall buildings (surrounded). N: shorter (open vista).
; ================================================================

